\c 84
\s Mufaro uri paimba yaMwari
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. NeGititi. Kuvana vaKora. Pisarema.
\p
\v 1 Anodika sei matende enyu, Jehovha wedzihondo!
\p
\v 2 Mweya wangu unoshuva, zvirokwazvo unopanga vazhe dzaJehovha; moyo wangu nenyama yangu zvinodana kuna Mwari mupenyu.
\v 3 Zvirokwazvo dhimba yakawana imba, nenyenganyenga dendere rayo, painoisa vana vayo, aritari dzenyu, Jehovha wedzihondo, Mambo wangu, naMwari wangu.
\v 4 Vakaropafadzwa vanogara mumba menyu; vachagara vachikurumbidzai. Sera.
\v 5 Wakaropafadzwa munhu uyo simba rake riri mamuri, mune nzira huru mumoyo mavo.
\v 6 Vanopfuura nemumupata weBhaka vanouita tsime; nemaropafadzo anozadza nhuruka.
\v 7 Vanofamba kubva pasimba kuenda pasimba; \add umwe neumwe\add* aonekwe pamberi paMwari paZiyoni.
\p
\v 8 Jehovha, Mwari wedzihondo, inzwa munyengetero wangu; ipai nzeve, Mwari waJakove. Sera.
\v 9 Tarirai, Mwari, nhovo yedu, mugotarisa chiso chemuzodzwa wenyu.
\v 10 Nokuti zuva pavazhe dzenyu riri nani pane churu. Ndinosarudza kuva pakurinda mukova muimba yaMwari pane kugara mumatende euipi.
\v 11 Nokuti Jehovha Mwari izuva nenhovo; Jehovha achapa nyasha nerukudzo; haanganyimi zvakanaka kune vanofamba nekururama.
\p
\v 12 Jehovha wedzihondo, wakaropafadzwa munhu anovimba nemwi.